gram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressed in a hot pink suit and with her blond tresses curled, Gutman's style was reminiscent of Reese Witherspoon's \\\"Elle Woods\\\" outfit in a fictitious congressional scene in the 2003 film \\\"Legally Blonde 2.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reese_Witherspoon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reese Witherspoon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reese_Witherspoon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reese_Witherspoon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hot pink suit\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"her blond tresses\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"Gutman's style\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"a fictitious congressional scene\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2003 film\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Legally Blonde\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Related ArticlesBeauty FeaturesIs 'the Algorithm' Killing Beauty?Beauty FeaturesWhy Black Beauty Founders Are Turning to TikTok Shop to Build Brands Beaming with a smile throughout her brief remarks, Gutman, who is cofounder of the She Is Cheval label, informed attendees of knowing from a very young age what she wanted to do with her life.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Algorithm' Killing Beauty?Beauty FeaturesWhy Black Beauty Founders\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"TikTok Shop\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"her brief remarks\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"Gutman\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"cofounder\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"Cheval label\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\"