\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, the designer explained that she had signed an employment contract that included a noncompete clause in 2011 at the age of 25.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"the designer\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"an employment contract\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"a noncompete clause\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The contract was with JLM Couture, which she did not identify by name.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The contract\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"JLM Couture\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"name\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She continued to design her namesake wedding gowns until 2020.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her namesake wedding gowns\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That same year JLM took legal action against her for allegedly locking out the company from the \\\"Hayley Paige\\\"social mediaaccounts and violating a noncompete deal, among other alleged infractions.)\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"JLM\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"legal action\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Hayley Paige\\\"social mediaaccounts\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"a noncompete deal\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"other alleged infractions\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Opening the event, the senator had suggested that noncompetes impact 1 in 5 American workers in a variety of fields including \\\"doggie day care\