ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gutman\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4499}, {\"ngram\": \"victimhood\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4550}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4569}, {\"ngram\": \"her trade\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4647}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessary skill set\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She and JLM Couture had been warring since 2020 in the courts.\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"JLM Couture\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4722}, {\"ngram\": \"the courts\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In January, the Second Circuit Court rejected a six-factor social media account ownership test and vacated a preliminary injunction that had awarded JLM control of her social media accounts.\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4782, \"end\": 4796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Court_of_Appeals_for_the_Second_Circuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Second Circuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Court_of_Appeals_for_the_Second_Circuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Court_of_Appeals_for_the_Second_Circuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-factor social media account ownership test\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"a preliminary injunction\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"JLM control\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4926}, {\"ngram\": \"her social media accounts\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 4955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that time, the court sided with her attorneys' argument that ownership should be determined \\\"like any other form of property,\\\" by determining who owned the account at the moment of its creation and then evaluating whether that owner sold or transferred the account.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 4960, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"her attorneys' argument\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5015}, {\"ngram\": \"ownership\", \"from\": 5021, \"to\": 5030}, {\"ngram\": \"any other form\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5072}, {\"ngram\": \"property\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5084}, {\"ngram\": \"the account\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"its creation\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"that owner\", \"from\": 5182, \"to\": 5192}, {\"ngram\": \"the account\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, the designer had been sidelined from competing with JLM until the end of her contract, or using \\\"Hayley Paige\\\" in advertising.\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5332, \"end\": 5338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Ackley_Bridge\", \"score\": 0.6647747900996511, \"rank\": 0.5038738549923267, \"text\": \"Hayley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Ackley_Bridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Ackley_Bridge\"}, {\"begin\": 5339, \"end\": 5344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Matthews\", \"score\": 0.9999999999490683, \"rank\": 5.024169228058806e-11, \"text\": \"Paige\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Matthews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Matthews\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the designer\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5247}, {\"ngram\": \"JLM\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5297, \"to\": 5304}, {\"ngram\": \"her contract\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5320}, {\"ngram\": \"advertising\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5360}]}, {\"se